{"tid":1178456,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保安局局長李家超被問到如果中央提出移交疑犯，行政長官能否拒絕，他回應，行政長官有權處理或不處理任何個案","createTime":"2019-05-30T12:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T12:21:38.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f6564feb64b0384b29f755570d973e96f2c053f","tid":1178456,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"政府就修訂《逃犯條例》提出6項建議，包括提高移交門檻，罪行刑期由3年增至7年或以上。保安局局長李家超被問到如果中央提出移交疑犯，行政長官能否拒絕，他回應，行政長官有權處理或不處理任何個案，特首在作出決定時要按照《逃犯條例》的限制，亦要符合所有香港的法律。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">被問到台灣殺人案及商人劉鑾雄在澳門涉及的案件，一旦需要移交，由當地哪個部門提出，李家超說，移交逃犯請求必須由當地能夠代表中央機關提出，特區政府收到有關要求時，亦會了解清楚提出的機構是否由代表當地的中央機關提出。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李家超亦被問到，方案今次是否最後一次微調，不會再有調整空間，他說，在考慮各方意見後，認為現時的方案是最適當。他說聽了不同意見，有些人建議移交門檻的罪行刑期應在3年或7年，亦有意見認為應增至10年，政府綜合考慮後，這是最平衡的做法。"},{"pid":"dd6eeb33a6588f034b475962ae13c86046c3f786","tid":1178456,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1460165-20190530.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1460165-20190530.htm&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1R21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=2b70604d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1460165-20190530.htm&h=2f2fb638\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1460165-20190530.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ae746dd118682bb63e18a3bf3ed74b22a88076ed","tid":1178456,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:05:45.000Z","msg":"等仆街啦"},{"pid":"3077806c594aa8f8cf32a3508f325a7a2e067827","tid":1178456,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:06:13.000Z","msg":"唔用個別事件喇？"},{"pid":"c7d4ab5597c333a237313b6197897107313a7a24","tid":1178456,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5d1eee3ac29afc6b2b817c4c547821c2ede91e","tid":1178456,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:21:38.000Z","msg":"行政長官係由中央委任<br />\n行政長官要向中央負責"}]}